column1: #park identification is an identifier for the park
#latitude, longitude are given in decimal degrees e.g. 41.152712, -8.609297
#elevation is given in metres (m) with no decimal places. When not given, consider 0
#park description is a descriptive name for the park e.g. "Trindade"
#max number of bicycles - maximum park capability for bicycles e.g. 10
#max number of escooters - maximum park capability for escooters e.g. 20
#park input voltage - the park input voltage measured in Volts (V) e.g. 220V
#park input current - the park input current measured in Amperes (A) e.g. 16A
